*French: [[barre]] ''f'' (1)
*German: [[Steuer]] ''n''
*Hungarian: [[kormány]]
*Romanian: [[cârmă]] ''f''
*Slovenian: [[krma]] ''f''

===Etymology===
Old English ''helm''
====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

#(''Archaic'') A [[helmet]].

